696
00:37:06,120 --> 00:37:07,553
Right out here.

697
00:37:12,080 --> 00:37:13,877
Morton, this is President Bartlet.

698
00:37:14,200 --> 00:37:15,679
-Hey, Morton.
-Wow!

699
00:37:16,200 --> 00:37:18,077
-Well said. Is that the turkey?
-Yes.

700
00:37:18,200 --> 00:37:19,189
-You're pardoned.
-Sir?

701
00:37:19,520 --> 00:37:21,033
-What do you want?
-You know....

702
00:37:21,440 --> 00:37:24,079
