then go back to your school...

707
00:37:35,040 --> 00:37:37,429
...and insist to be better prepared
to go out in the world.

708
00:37:37,960 --> 00:37:39,996
You can't pardon a turkey?

709
00:37:40,120 --> 00:37:42,270
No. I'll tell you what I can do.

710
00:37:42,800 --> 00:37:45,075
I'm drafting this turkey
into military service.

711
00:37:45,200 --> 00:37:47,156
In the meantime,
somebody will draft a check...

712
00:37:47,480 --> 00:37:51,439
...with my signature on it so the folks
