719
00:38:03,160 --> 00:38:06,152
I'm going to step out there
and begin the singing and lute playing.

720
00:38:06,480 --> 00:38:07,629
Whatever.

721
00:38:08,320 --> 00:38:09,196
I assume you've heard.

722
00:38:09,520 --> 00:38:13,638
By the way, the Latin word
for yam is Dioscorea.

723
00:38:14,160 --> 00:38:14,797
You've heard?

724
00:38:15,320 --> 00:38:17,550
-About the Chinese refugees?
-They escaped.

725
00:38:18,080 --> 00:38:19,149
I know. Can you believe it?

726
00:38:19,280 --> 00:38:21,475
No, neither one of us
can believe it, sir.

727
00:38:22,000 --> 00:38:25,310
That detention center was being guarded
by the California National Guard.

728
00:38:25,840 --> 00:38:27,478
Now what doe's it say
about our Reserve Army?

729
00:38:28,000 --> 00:38:29,319
That 83 men, women and children...

730
00:38:29,840 --> 00:38:33,037
...who haven't eaten in two months,
staged a prison break?

731
00:38:34,160 --> 00:38:35,752
Let me read this.

732
00:38:36,520 --> 00:38:39,159
" Over three and a half centuries ago,
strengthened by faith...

733
00:38:39,480 --> 00:38:41,038
...and bound by a common desire
for liberty...

734
00:38:41,760 --> 00:38:45,673
...a small band of Pilgrims
sought out a place in the New World...

735
00:38:46,000 --> 00:38:49,117
...where they could worship
according to their own beliefs.

736
00:38:52,240 --> 00:38:55,676
Therefore, l, Josiah Bartlet,
President of the United States...

737
00:38:56,200 --> 00:38:58,270
... by virtue of the authority
and laws vested in me...

738
00:38:58,800 --> 00:39:02,793
...do hereby proclaim this to be
a National Day of Thanksgiving. "

739
00:39:04,240 --> 00:39:06,037
I'll see you out there, sir.

740
00:39:11,280 --> 00:39:15,034
You asked the governor
to stand down the 22nd Division.

741
00:39:15,440 --> 00:39:17,590
And call in the Red Cross.

742
00:39:18,480 --> 00:39:19,799
We didn't do anything illegal.

743
00:39:20,120 --> 00:39:23,271
You're not involved
in any massive criminal conspiracy.

744
00:39:23,800 --> 00:39:26,951
I wasn't letting them go,
and we needed to help China save face.

745
00:39:27,080 --> 00:39:32,154
They can tell their people that the mighty
American military was overpowered by--

746
00:39:35,400 --> 00:39:37,960
So the guy passed the test, huh?

747
00:39:38,960 --> 00:39:41,952
You think I would have sent him back
if he failed catechism?

748
00:39:42,080 --> 00:39:43,274
Let me tell you something.

749
00:39:43,800 --> 00:39:45,199
We can be the world's policeman.

750
00:39:45,520 --> 00:39:49,035
We can be the world's bank,
the world's factory, the world's farm.

751
00:39:49,760 --> 00:39:52,149
What doe's it mean
if we're not also...?

752
00:39:54,000 --> 00:39:56,560
They made it to the New World, Josh.

753
00:39:57,080 --> 00:39:59,150
You know what I get to do now?

754
00:39:59,280 --> 00:40:01,919
I get to proclaim
a National Day of Thanksgiving.

755
00:40:02,240 --> 00:40:05,516
Ladies and gentlemen, boys and girls,
